- Dunno.

843
01:15:02,550 --> 01:15:05,510
- Where can l reach you tomorrow?
- Dunno.

844
01:15:05,510 --> 01:15:08,270
The hotels are crawling with tourists.

845
01:15:08,270 --> 01:15:11,150
My friend in Montmartre has a big flat.

846
01:15:11,150 --> 01:15:14,270
- Not Montmartre.
- No, not Montmartre.

847
01:15:14,270 --> 01:15:16,030
Why not?

848
01:15:16,030 --> 01:15:18,830
