849
01:15:18,830 --> 01:15:20,870
Try Zumbart's Swedish girl.

850
01:15:20,870 --> 01:15:23,830
Rue Campagne Premiere?

851
01:15:23,830 --> 01:15:25,790
Call me there tomorrow.

852
