868
01:16:56,270 --> 01:16:57,910
No, l like that one.

869
01:16:57,910 --> 01:17:00,830
l thought you didn't like music.

870
01:17:00,830 --> 01:17:05,310
This one's OK.
My dad was a clarinettist.

871
01:17:05,310 --> 01:17:08,550
My dad was a brilliant clarinet-player.

872
01:17:08,550 --> 01:17:10,710
Want to turn in?

873
01:17:10,710 --> 01:17:12,910
Sleeping's so sad.

874
01:17:12,910 --> 01:17:14,590
