903
01:20:31,150 --> 01:20:35,590
- l said you were here.
- Are you crazy?

904
01:20:35,590 --> 01:20:38,350
No, l'm fine.

905
01:20:39,630 --> 01:20:41,710
No, l'm not.

906
01:20:41,710 --> 01:20:45,030
l don't want to go with you.

907
01:20:45,030 --> 01:20:47,230
l knew it.

908
01:20:47,230 --> 01:20:48,430
l don't know.

909
01:20:48,430 --> 01:20:51,670
l just talked about myself,
and you, yourself.

910
01:20:51,670 --> 01:20:53,190
l'm so stupid.

911
01:20:53,190 --> 01:20:56,950
You should've talked about me,
and me, about you.

912
01:20:56,950 --> 01:21:00,510
l don't want to be in love with you.

913
01:21:01,470 --> 01:21:05,310
That's why l called the police.

914
01:21:05,310 --> 01:21:10,590
l stayed with you
to see if l was in love with you.

915
01:21:10,590 --> 01:21:13,430
Or if l wasn't.

916
01:21:15,710 --> 01:21:18,710
