919
01:21:23,710 --> 01:21:27,390
And since l'm being cruel to you,

920
01:21:27,390 --> 01:21:32,030
it proves l'm not in love with you.

921
01:21:32,030 --> 01:21:35,070
They say there's no happy love.

922
01:21:35,070 --> 01:21:38,150
lf l loved you...

923
01:21:38,150 --> 01:21:40,030
lt's too complicated!

924
01:21:40,030 --> 01:21:44,510
On the contrary,
there's no unhappy love.

925
01:21:44,510 --> 01:21:47,950
l want people to let me be.

926
01:21:47,950 --> 01:21:49,630
l'm independent.

927
01:21:49,630 --> 01:21:53,990
- Maybe you love me.
- You think you are. You're not.

928
01:21:53,990 --> 01:21:55,990
