943
01:22:56,950 --> 01:22:59,830
l can look at the walls.

944
01:22:59,830 --> 01:23:01,190
Damn, Berruti!

945
01:23:02,910 --> 01:23:05,590
Hey, amigo! l'll just park.

946
01:23:08,590 --> 01:23:10,630
- Cops are coming.
- Your money!

947
01:23:10,630 --> 01:23:13,070
