951
01:23:23,430 --> 01:23:24,990
l'm tired.

952
01:23:24,990 --> 01:23:26,550
l want to sleep.

953
01:23:26,550 --> 01:23:28,030
You're nuts!

954
01:23:28,030 --> 01:23:31,710
Damn the police. l'll save my neck.

955
01:23:31,710 --> 01:23:36,430
l shouldn't be thinking of her
but l can't help it.

956
01:23:36,430 --> 01:23:39,310
Want my automatic?

957
01:23:41,270 --> 01:23:43,470
- Don't be stupid!
- Get lost!

958
